ğŸ§ª **Impact**  
This work demonstrates how deep learning and clustering can complement each other in hyperspectral image analysis. Our framework contributes toward scalable, efficient remote sensing pipelinesâ€”powering future applications in **environmental monitoring**, **agriculture**, and **disaster response**.
